N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 ยง 189.4 - Marking of parts

State Regulations

Except as provided in section
189.3
(b)(2) and
(3)
of this Part, all parts of any CWD
susceptible animal imported into New York, or packages or containers containing
such parts, shall be affixed with a legible label bearing the following
information: the species of animal, the state or province and country where the
animal was taken, and the name and address of the person who took the
animal. Notes
